This is a Cinnamon applet designed to look like the mintMenu.

Change log:
2.6.9
Removed "uninstall application"
Added GUI favorites editing

2.6
Allowed user-defined package manager (Synaptic by default)
Allowed custom favorites list with separators
Added "uninstall application" on right-click

2.5
Allowed GUI editing of places
Searches web when there is no search result

2.4
Allowed different sizes for different icons

2.3
Allowed changing places

2.2
Added Settings Editor

2.1
Allowed changing icon size

2.0
Added favorites panel

1.1
Added "Terminal" button in left panel

1.0
Initial release